lead_paragraph: MURPHY--Elinor C.,87, of San Diego, CA, formerly of East 20th St. in New York City, died in her sleep on January 26, 2016. Mother of Jim and Tom. She was predeceased by her husband Albert. Calling hours, January 28, 2-5pm and 7-9pm at Andrett Funeral Home, 199 Bleecker St., NYC. Services Friday, 10:30am, Epiphany Church, 2nd Ave. and 22nd St. Burial to follow at Calverton National Cemetery on Long Island. 1/3
